VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT didReceive\s+challenge.*completionHandler\(\.useCredential|allowInvalidCertificates
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SecTrustEvaluate|SecTrustEvaluateWithError
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects URLSession trust challenge handling patterns indicating bypass risk.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for iOS URLSession Trust Bypass Pattern.
